7.4 FLAG VALUES
===============

The 'flags' parameter in all the _call_*_ functions is one of G_VOID,
G_SCALAR, or G_ARRAY, which indicate the call context, OR'ed together
with a bit mask of any combination of the other G_* symbols defined
below.

