60.2.6.2 Examples
.................

 /(\w+) \g1/;    # Finds a duplicated word, (e.g. "cat cat").
 /(\w+) \1/;     # Same thing; written old-style.
 /(.)(.)\g2\g1/;  # Match a four letter palindrome (e.g. "ABBA").


